parts.text: *Meet the Medic!*  Jawohl!  *Ahahahaha!*  So, you vant to know about me?  I am ze Medic!  And I… *practice medicine!*  Not like those *other* doctors, no.  *They* are just *fixers*. I am an *improver!*  I take ze broken and make zem… *better!*  Sometimes… *much better!*  *Ahahahaha!*  You see zat Heavy over dere?  He vas nearly dead!  But I, I gave him a *new heart!*  A *mega baboon heart!*  Zat vas doctor-assisted… *enhancement!*  *Ahahahaha!*  And ze Spy?  He needed a little… *recalibration*.  So I connected his brain to a potato!  *Ahahahaha!*  It's all about ze science!  Ze *exciting* science!  I do not care about ethics, only *results!*  So, if you need a little… *improving*, come see me! But be warned… my methods are… *unconventional*.  *Ahahahaha!*
